~ 𝐏𝐬𝐚𝐥𝐦𝐬 𝟏𝟐𝟕:𝟒 ~⁣
“𝐋𝐢𝐤𝐞 𝐚𝐫𝐫𝐨𝐰𝐬 𝐢𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐚 𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐫 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐫𝐞𝐧 𝐛𝐨𝐫𝐧 𝐢𝐧 𝐨𝐧𝐞’𝐬 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐭𝐡.”

𝐌𝐞𝐫𝐫𝐲 𝐂𝐡𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐦𝐚𝐬!⁣
𝐉𝐨𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬, 𝐟𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐟𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬, 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐦𝐚𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐝𝐚𝐲! ⁣
⁣
- 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝗪𝐢𝐥𝐬𝐨𝐧𝐬 ❤️

Welcome to the world, Easton! ❤️

We did it! 100,000 subscribers on @youtube! 🎉 Could not have done this without the support of my wife @katlynwilsonnyc, my pastor @mikesignorelli_ , and my amazing church @v1church 🔥 There aren’t YouTube play buttons in heaven, so while this is a cool milestone, it’s all about SOULS. ONE person coming to know Jesus is enough. We are committed to bringing people into the kingdom through salvation in Jesus, and deep discipleship through the local church. So if we can use YouTube, Instagram, or TikTok to do that, that’s what we’re gonna do! Next stop, 1 million! 🙏
